\mathbb{R}^N
 (i\partial _t+\Delta)\,u=0\mbox{ ,}\quad u(0,x)=f
f\in L^2(\mathbb{R}^N)
u(t,x)=e^{it\Delta}f
\frac{1}{T}\int_0^Te^{it\Delta}fdt\rightarrow 0\quad\mbox{in }L^2(\mathbb{R}^N)
P:\,f\mapsto\frac{1}{T}\int_0^Te^{it\Delta}fdt
P\circ e^{it\Delta}=P
e^{it\Delta}\circ P=P\quad \forall t\in\mathbb{R}.
Im\,P=Fix\{e^{it\Delta}\}_{t\geq 0}=Ker\,i\Delta=\{0\}
P=0
{e^{it\Delta}}
